227	///
228	/// It can be parsed from a `String`, using `;` as separator between each parameter and `=` as separator between a key and its value.
229	///
230	/// Keys can have multiple values, using `|` as a separator between them. An iterator for these can be obtained with [`Parameters::values`].
231	///
232	/// Example:
233	/// ```
