24	/// The [`Queryable`](crate::query::Queryable)s to which a query from
25	/// a [`Session::get`](crate::Session::get) or a [`Querier::get`](crate::query::Querier::get)
26	/// is delivered.
27	///
28	/// * [`QueryTarget::All`] makes the query be delivered to all the matching queryables.
29	/// * [`QueryTarget::AllComplete`] makes the query be delivered to all the matching queryables
30	///   which are marked as "complete" with
31	///   [`QueryableBuilder::complete`](crate::query::QueryableBuilder::complete).
32	/// * [`QueryTarget::BestMatching`] (default) makes the data to be requested from the
33	///   queryable(s) selected by zenoh to get the fastest and most complete reply.
34	///
35	/// It is set by [`SessionGetBuilder::target`](crate::session::SessionGetBuilder::target)
36	/// or [`QuerierBuilder::target`](crate::query::QuerierBuilder::target) methods.
